values: Today is my first day back online. Ive been busy moving, cutting downt trees in my yard, building a privacy fence, and i found a new job Im working at the Domino's Pizza down the street from my house i started at $5.50 but in two more day (after only 5 days of work) i will be making $6.00 an hour. So krogers can kiss my butt!
Tomorrow we start moving to Trenton. I think it will suck. I am not looking forward to moving away from my friends even though i will still see them.
Today i started my live Journal. Me and my friend went job hunting today we are finally quiting Krogers.
